      "id": "PopularPost284812",
      "post_content": "Kryptnyt said: *Well, he's pretty much the only creature in the game I can think of that can attack for 20 on turn 6 with no other plays.*  \n[Sokenzan Spellblade](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sokenzan Spellblade) and 6 Mountains is exactly 20 damage attacking turn 6. (Both cards require you to be on the draw.)  \nInteresting how similar those two are: Both are Ogre [Flame Spirit](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Spirit)s that get +18/+0 for six mana and six cards.  \n  \nTrying another route...  \n[Stromkirk Noble](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stromkirk Noble): 0,1,2,3,4,5,6 = 21 on turn 7  \n[Slith Firewalker](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slith Firewalker): 0,1,2,3,4,5,6 = 21 on turn 7  \n[Bloodcrazed Neonate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodcrazed Neonate): 0,0,2,3,4,5,6 = 20 on turn 7  \n[Erdwal Ripper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Erdwal Ripper): 0,0,2,3,4,5,6 = 20 on turn 7  \n[Markov Blademaster](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Markov Blademaster): 0,0,0,1+2,3+4,5+6 = 21 on turn 6!",
      "posted_by": "HuntingDrake",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost284812\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Kryptnyt said: <i>Well, he's pretty much the only creature in the game I can think of that can attack for 20 on turn 6 with no other plays.</i><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sokenzan Spellblade\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sokenzan Spellblade\">Sokenzan Spellblade</a> and 6 Mountains is exactly 20 damage attacking turn 6. (Both cards require you to be on the draw.)<br/>Interesting how similar those two are: Both are Ogre <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Flame Spirit\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flame Spirit\">Flame Spirit</a>s that get +18/+0 for six mana and six cards.<br/><br/>Trying another route...<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Stromkirk Noble\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stromkirk Noble\">Stromkirk Noble</a>: 0,1,2,3,4,5,6 = 21 on turn 7<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Slith Firewalker\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Slith Firewalker\">Slith Firewalker</a>: 0,1,2,3,4,5,6 = 21 on turn 7<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bloodcrazed Neonate\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodcrazed Neonate\">Bloodcrazed Neonate</a>: 0,0,2,3,4,5,6 = 20 on turn 7<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Erdwal Ripper\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Erdwal Ripper\">Erdwal Ripper</a>: 0,0,2,3,4,5,6 = 20 on turn 7<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Markov Blademaster\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Markov Blademaster\">Markov Blademaster</a>: 0,0,0,1+2,3+4,5+6 = 21 on turn 6!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '284812'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy26712\">HuntingDrake</span>\r\n                                (12/7/2012 11:15:11 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
