    {
      "id": "PopularPost122725",
      "post_content": "+3/+0 for just one red mana? That's actually quite strong. You could for example discard [anger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=anger), then you have a 5/3 with haste. Or you discard some [Fiery Temper](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Temper). They cost another red mana to play with madness, but can then take out possible blockers to clear the path, or simply burn more at your opponent. Like, discard two fiery temper while your opponent has no blockers, and you'd deal a total of 14 damage with this guy (he'd have 8 power and the fiery temper would deal another 6).  \nOr discard anything with unearth, or flashback, or recover, or whatever.  \n  \nHe's not perfect, but there are easily decks where he can do a fine job. Also good for hellbent decks. Or [Dark Suspicions](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Suspicions) and [Mindstorm Crown](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindstorm Crown) and many others.",
      "posted_by": "majinara",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost122725\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">+3/+0 for just one red mana? That's actually quite strong. You could for example discard <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"anger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=anger\">anger</a>, then you have a 5/3 with haste. Or you discard some <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fiery Temper\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fiery Temper\">Fiery Temper</a>. They cost another red mana to play with madness, but can then take out possible blockers to clear the path, or simply burn more at your opponent. Like, discard two fiery temper while your opponent has no blockers, and you'd deal a total of 14 damage with this guy (he'd have 8 power and the fiery temper would deal another 6).<br/>Or discard anything with unearth, or flashback, or recover, or whatever.<br/><br/>He's not perfect, but there are easily decks where he can do a fine job. Also good for hellbent decks.  Or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Dark Suspicions\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dark Suspicions\">Dark Suspicions</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mindstorm Crown\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mindstorm Crown\">Mindstorm Crown</a> and many others.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '122725'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"p