    {
      "id": "PopularPost251307",
      "post_content": "I remember this card, I remember not drafting him, I remember not playing him, and I remember being very happy when my opponent used his ability to discard a Kamahl Pit Fighter. I understand Red is the most random color but the discard mechanic in Odyssey rewarded Blue, Green, White and Black and it nerfed Red. So many spells that could've been game breaking had Random discard and it made playing Red very unreliable. Thanks Wizards for taking a good mechanic and leaving one color out in the cold.",
      "posted_by": "vantha",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost251307\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">I remember this card, I remember not drafting him, I remember not playing him, and I remember being very happy when my opponent used his ability to discard a Kamahl Pit Fighter. I understand Red is the most random color but the discard mechanic in Odyssey rewarded Blue, Green, White and Black and it nerfed Red. So many spells that could've been game breaking had Random discard and it made playing Red very unreliable. Thanks Wizards for taking a good mechanic and leaving one color out in the cold.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '251307'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy73424\">vantha</span>\r\n                                (6/15/2012 7:56:56 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/